
1. PRODUCT IDENTIFICATION
------------------------------------------------------------
Product Name: Premium Motor Spirit (PMS)
Common Name: Petrol / Gasoline
Standard: Nigerian PMS Specification (NNPC / SON)
Supply Source: Refinery‑linked allocation & approved depots
Delivery Mode: Depot pickup or delivered‑to‑site

------------------------------------------------------------
2. TYPICAL PMS SPECIFICATIONS
------------------------------------------------------------

Parameter                         Unit        Typical Value     Standard Limit
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Research Octane Number (RON)      –              91 min              ≥ 91
Motor Octane Number (MON)         –              82 min              ≥ 81
Density @ 15°C                    kg/m³         720–780            715–780
Reid Vapour Pressure (RVP)        kPa            45–60              45–60
Sulphur Content                   ppm            50 max             ≤ 50
Benzene Content                   % vol          1.0 max            ≤ 1.0
Oxygen Content                    % mass         2.7 max            ≤ 2.7
Lead Content                      g/L              Nil                Nil
Colour                            –          Clear / Water‑white     Clear
Copper Corrosion                  –               1A                 1A
Gum Content (Unwashed)            mg/100ml        5 max             ≤ 5

